title: Q&A With Jessi! Season Finale
description: It's a break, not a break-up! Jessi goes solo in this season finale and is answering all of your burning questions. From how she handles things in her salon to how she navigates relationships. Grab your must-have drink and then settle in as Dr. Jessi dishes out the therapy you didn't know you needed!
